title: T.I. - Swagga Like Us (Remix) (G-Mix) (October 2008)
description:
"Swagga Like Us" is the latest single from the King of the South T.I. it was already a blazing hot track with Kanye West, Jay Z & Lil Wayne, but it's even better now that it's featuring Louisiana's own Bezzletine A.K.A. Mr. G-Mix! If you like this be sure to check out Bezzletine's other tracks too. Exclusive FREE mixtape coming soon. Look out for it on a torrent site near you!

This is the the hottest song in October 2008! You have to check it out!

And don't forget to SEED. 

If you like it, SEED it! If you don't like it, SEED it!
